// About — cost data source
"about_cost_source" = "Cost computed locally from ~/.claude/projects & ~/.codex/logs_2.sqlite";
"about_cost_source_help" = "Anthropic cost is derived by parsing assistant messages in your local Claude Code session JSONL files (~/.claude/projects/*/*.jsonl), then multiplying input/output/cache tokens by the published Claude pricing.\n\nOpenAI cost reads total_usage_tokens from ~/.codex/logs_2.sqlite and applies the Codex model pricing.\n\nNothing is sent to any network — the calculation happens entirely on your Mac. Subscription plans (Claude Max, ChatGPT Pro) charge a flat fee; the number shown is what an API equivalent of the same usage would cost.";

